# Local dev: leave VITE_API_URL unset — Vite proxy uses /api → http://localhost:5000 (vite.config.js).
#
# Vercel (FRONTEND project only): set in Dashboard → Environment Variables (do NOT use placeholder text).
# Value = open your BACKEND Vercel project → copy production HTTPS URL → add /api at the end.
# Real shape looks like: https://lms-backend-abc123.vercel.app/api
